{"tid":1520924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Bridgefy Plan B (斷網時可使用)","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T04:28:34.000Z","uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8091f0e8cfe3397c480c6172ad7b7a7c479135d4","tid":1520924,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:57:52.000Z","msg":"【緊急整合】用真身號碼喺tg講發夢即刻刪除AC，教埋你重開<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497612</a><br />\n話說之前睇完呢個巴打講話可以用textnow開左個美國號碼<br />\n<br />\n呢家港共政府可以隨時ddos連登，到時可能甚至會斷網都有機會（多人都會搞到網絡不穩）<br />\n所以呢家我地就需要使用Bridgefy呢個app去係網絡不穩時溝通<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇呢篇（或者之前有個巴打ＰＯ過有關文章）<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E3%80%90%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E3%80%91%E6%96%B7%E7%B6%B2%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BA%92%E5%82%B3%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF+Bridgefy%E3%80%80+%E9%87%8E%E9%A4%90%E5%A5%BD%E5%B9%AB%E6%89%8B%EF%BC%81%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88Wi+Fi%E3%80%81%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2-B00k02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25B7%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%2582%25B3%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25AF%2BBridgefy%25E3%2580%2580%2B%25E9%2587%258E%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E6%2589%258B%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%25AF%258B%25E9%25A0%2588Wi%2BFi%25E3%2580%2581%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%25B6%25B2-B00k02&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2c3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=da00553e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E3%80%90%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8%E3%80%91%E6%96%B7%E7%B6%B2%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BA%92%E5%82%B3%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%AF+Bridgefy%E3%80%80+%E9%87%8E%E9%A4%90%E5%A5%BD%E5%B9%AB%E6%89%8B%EF%BC%81%E6%AF%8B%E9%A0%88Wi+Fi%E3%80%81%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2-B00k02</a><br />\n<br />\n岩岩有巴打開過POST話需要使用到太空卡去用呢個APP先係最穩陣，但係岩岩上網睇到有人話可以用我地之前係textnow開個個號碼用落bridgefy到，咁就變就太空號碼，唔洗出去買太空卡咁煩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（Ｐ牌，有錯請屌，小弟不才無呢方面知識，上網睇到同大家講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"9e6093a95f35ac5016d6f584ce1b84bbbf957593","tid":1520924,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"(1/10)"},{"pid":"e5c6edf0faedb21732ffbae98cba66f0b85800b0","tid":1520924,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"(2/10)"},{"pid":"9d27f3990cc21afae716a70ec18aba9b028b687b","tid":1520924,"uid":307414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:24:08.000Z","msg":"(3/10)"},{"pid":"70742849c5e0c516707686b1625cccc4ee24b6ac","tid":1520924,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"亂作個number<br />\nresend兩次驗證碼之後就可以skip電話號碼"}]}